title: 3: Moments Asking My Mom What You’re Scared to Ask Yours
itunes:title: Moments Asking My Mom What You’re Scared to Ask Yours
description: Hey beautiful people, I won’t lie I was super nervous to record this. But I’m so glad I did, I think my mom and I both learned a lot from each other. So here’s the moment we asked my mom all the scary questions we’ve always wanted answers to.
itunes:author: Lexi Hidalgo
dc:creator: Lexi Hidalgo
